        &kp TILDE  &kp GRAVE  &kp SQT   &kp DQT    &kp MINUS    &kp PLUS   &sk LSHFT  &sk LCTRL  &sk LALT  &sk LCMD
&trans  &kp BSLH   &kp PIPE   &kp SEMI  &kp COMMA  &kp UNDER    &kp EQUAL  &kp DOT    &kp COLON  &kp PIPE  &kp SLASH  &trans
